{"tid":1742244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"條能樣竟然冇事","createTime":"2019-11-20T16:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T16:52:15.000Z","uid":333193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"275de993c6e8a4a3b9d3fe23b23c7292c6cf31a7","tid":1742244,"uid":333193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:46:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/singapore/story20191120-1006922?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Facebook#Echobox=1574262791\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Frealtime%2Fsingapore%2Fstory20191120-1006922%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3DFacebook%23Echobox%3D1574262791&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=e6b4b9b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zaobao.com/realtime/singapore/story20191120-1006922?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=Facebook#Echobox=1574262791</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3255247867879692&amp;id=160823460655497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3255247867879692%26id%3D160823460655497&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzi9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=1f18dd99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3255247867879692&amp;id=160823460655497</a><br />\n<br />\n（早报讯）香港茶餐厅老板杨官华（Alex Yeung）日前因涉及在新加坡举行集会，邀请公众探讨香港目前局势，结果护照遭新加坡警方扣留、协助调查。<br />\n<br />\n警方今晚（20日）回答媒体询问时说，有人呼吁新加坡释放杨官华，并且不要对他采取进一步行动。<br />\n<br />\n杨官华因举行未经批准的公众集会，抵触公共秩序法（Public Order Act），被给予严厉警告。目前，杨官华已被遣返，并且今后不可在未经移民局批准的情况下入境我国。"},{"pid":"df542c6f3f5895d1d2fd59c446d1331fe6b58291","tid":1742244,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:47:39.000Z","msg":"戰役過後，痛定思痛，認清現實，重新出發(抗爭五部曲-前言)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742018</a>"},{"pid":"8496cd54c181d42ef38efab37d4c64ee8034cb3e","tid":1742244,"uid":249885,"li